James E. KENNEDY, Appellant, v. Uzziel S. WHITCOMB and Alice M. Whitcomb, Debtors-Appellees. No. 173. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. May 1, 1946. Francis D. Foley and Samuel H. Roth-man, both of Burlington, Vt., for appellant. Consuelo Northrop Bailey and J. H. Ma-comber, Jr., both of Burlington, Vt., for appellees.

Before SWAN, CLARK, and WOOD-BURY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The order is affirmed on the opinion of the District Court, 61 F.Supp. 942.
